CATEGORIES:Exhibits,Lectures
DESCRIPTION:Can you see the Milky Way from your home? Experience a simple d
 emo of what prevents many of us from viewing a sky studded with thousands o
 f stars\, discover celestial wonders you can see only under a truly dark sk
 y\, and find out how you can help bring back the night.\n\n \n\nStar Famili
 es is a special series by Morehead Planetarium and Science Center that prov
 ides a live\, family-friendly fulldome experience. Arrive before your show 
 or stay after to journey through Morehead's interactive exhibits\, science 
 demo spaces\, and Cosmic Goods gift shop.\n\n \n\nThis program is recommend
 ed for families and children ages 7+. See you there!
DTEND:20260207T180000Z
