DESCRIPTION:Hone your AI detection skills in this hands-on workshop taught 
 via Zoom. Attendees will learn to distinguish authentic content from AI out
 put via practical activities and real-world examples of AI-generated scams\
 , deepfakes\, and misinformation.\n\nThis workshop is offered by the Univer
 sity Libraries and will be led by librarian Dayna Durbin\n\nThis workshop i
 s being offered remotely via Zoom only. You can register through the librar
 y calendar. Registrants will receive a Zoom link\; those on the waitlist wi
 ll not receive a Zoom link unless they are bumped up to a registered spot.
