CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:This presentation will explore how AI can help you quickly make
  sense of complex information by simplifying emails\, PDFs\, reports\, and 
 articles into what truly matters. Participants will learn how to extract ke
 y insights\, identify risks and next steps\, recognize potential bias\, and
  practice these skills through a guided exercise that turns a real document
  into a clear\, actionable summary.
DTEND:20260219T153000Z
DTSTAMP:20260306T215834Z
DTSTART:20260219T140000Z
