 e Shovel Down\; Be Holding\, winner of the PEN American Literary Jean Stein
  Award\; and Catalog of Unabashed Gratitude\, winner of the 2015 National B
 ook Critics Circle Award and the 2016 Kingsley Tufts Poetry Award. In addit
 ion to his poetry\, Ross has released three collections of essays—The Book 
