CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes,Lectures
DESCRIPTION:AI in Research: Driving Innovation Forward\n\nDiscover how arti
 ficial intelligence can streamline workflows\, uncover hidden patterns\, an
 d empower breakthroughs in your field. Learn practical applications of AI t
 hrough Odum Institute AIR series that can revolutionize your research proce
 ss.\n\nAI\, for example ChatGPT\, may be used to carry out some tasks commo
 nly used by social scientists. Examples include Pearson’s chi-square test\,
  Fisher’s exact test\, Student’s t-test\, power calculations and non-centra
 lity parameters. The quality of responses has varied to this point and may 
 continue to at the time of the class. Examples will be given.\n\nYou must h
 ave a UNC Chapel Hill Onyen to register and attend this course. No registra
 tion fees required but you must register to secure your spot and receive th
 e Zoom link.
