BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Relational Leadership @ Carolina offers the Relational Leadersh
 ip Institute as a professional development program that helps people build 
 teams and organizational cultures that prioritize connection\, engagement a
 nd well-being. Join the community of 500+ leaders who have participated sin
 ce 2019!\n\n \n\nThe Spring 2026 Four-Day Institute meets 8:30 a.m. - 4:30 
 p.m. each day\, in person at the Health Sciences Library: \n\nMonday\, Marc
 h 16\n\nTuesday\, March 17\n\nThursday\, March 26\n\nFriday\, March 27\n\n 
 \n\nThe series consists of 4 in-person sessions of 8 hours each. Each sessi
 on includes The curriculum includes a combination of large and small group 
 interactions to move through the four domains of Relational Leadership: man
 age self\; foster teamwork\; coach and develop\; and accelerate change. Par
 ticipants will complete asynchronous assignments between sessions\, includi
 ng skills practice and individual reflections on curricular content. The to
 tal time commitment for participants is 30 hours. Each session builds on th
 e next\, making attendance at all 4 dates a requirement to participate. \n\
 n \n\nQuestions? Contact Josh Hinson: qhinson@email.unc.edu\n\n \n\nSpots a
 re limited\, registration required.
