DESCRIPTION:Join us in person for the Accessible by April – POP Lab.  A dro
 p-in accessibility event designed to focus on Progress Over Perfection (POP
 ) as we all work towards a more digitally accessible Carolina. Roll up your
  sleeves and improve your own materials with support from DAO Consultants a
 nd Digital Accessibility Liaisons\, featuring exclusive POP-Up sessions and
  the POP Lab offering real-time answers so you can make real progress. Come
  for a session or stay for the day!\n\n \n\nRSVP to join us! All are welcom
