DESCRIPTION:Do you want to get better at searching in PubMed? This workshop
  covers advanced topics in PubMed\, including expanded searching features\,
  MeSH terms\, and clinical queries. It is ideal for students\, faculty or s
 taff who already have some familiarity with PubMed and literature searching
 .\n\n \n\nThis workshop is offered by the UNC Health Sciences Library and l
 ed by Katherine Howell.
