BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Exhibits
DESCRIPTION:Spend a spring evening learning more about documentary photogra
 phy during this month’s 2nd Friday ArtWalk inspired by Bill Bamberger: Boys
  Will Be Men. \nArtist Bill Bamberger will offer tours of the exhibition al
 ongside his faculty colleagues from the Duke Center for Documentary Studies
  while deputy director for curatorial affairs Peter Nisbet presents documen
 tary photographs from the Ackland’s collection in special study room sessio
 ns. \nSpace is limited for the study room sessions. There are two opportuni
 ties to join: Session 1 from 6:00–6:45pm and Session 2 from 7:00–7:45pm. Pl
 ease register below for your free ticket. \nThe event is free\, for all age
 s\, and all materials will be provided. The Museum will be open until 9 p.m
 . to see the exhibition and more.
DTEND:20260411T010000Z
