CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:REGISTRATION  IS OPEN!\n\n \n\nUNC 5K M.A.R.C.H. – Team Based M
 edWAR Style Race\n\nJoin the UNC Wilderness Medicine Program for the inaugu
 ral UNC 5K M.A.R.C.H. on April 11th\, 2026! This MedWAR style adventure rac
 e places teams of four on a 5K course through the UNC Outdoor Education Cen
 ter’s multi-use trails\, where they will encounter five wilderness medicine
  scenarios based on the M.A.R.C.H. protocol. Scenarios emphasize teamwork\,
  physical challenges\, and applied medical skills.\n\nThis event is open ex
 clusively to UNC affiliated participants (students\, faculty\, staff\, etc.
 ). Teams will be judged on scenario performance\, teamwork\, and style—spee
 d alone won’t win the day.\n\nStart/Finish & Parking Location:\nUNC Disc Go
 lf Course\n910 Raleigh Road\, Chapel Hill\, NC 27514\n\nTeams will begin vi
 a an 0800 rolling start\, departing every few minutes. Registration require
 s a complete team of four\, including your team name and all teammate names
 . We are planning for 20 total teams.\n\nFriends and family are welcome at 
 the start/finish area\, where we will have booths and activities. Please br
 ing your own food\, water\, and drinks. This event is rain or shine\, thoug
 h it may be cancelled for safety\; refunds cannot be issued if cancellation
  occurs.\n\nA waiver will be sent electronically before race day and must b
 e signed by all team members prior to participation.\n\nQuestions? Contact 
 Loboncaj@ad.unc.edu\n\n \n\nRegistration: https://apps2.research.unc.edu/ev
 ents/index.cfm?event=events.go&key=CD43
DTSTAMP:20260306T215835Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260411
LOCATION:
