BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:This 2-hour course will be held online only. Attendance is requ
 ired as it will not be recorded.\n\nIn this advanced topics course\, we wil
 l present several common use cases for automations using Qualtrics Workflow
