CATEGORIES:Meetings and Conferences
DESCRIPTION:The UNC Chapel Hill Out of the Darkness Campus Walk brings stud
 ents\, faculty\, and community members together to honor loved ones\, suppo
 rt one another\, and build connection around mental health and suicide prev
 ention. It’s a meaningful opportunity for students to show up for their pee
 rs\, raise awareness\, and help create a more caring campus community. The 
 walk is also a fundraising event\, with proceeds supporting the American Fo
 undation for Suicide Prevention’s work in education\, advocacy\, research\,
  and programs for those affected by suicide.\n\n \n\nRegistration starts at
  10:00 AM ET\, with the walk starting at 11:00 AM ET. The walk will take pl
 ace on UNC Chapel Hill Campus.
DTEND:20260418T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260306T215836Z
DTSTART:20260418T140000Z
LOCATION:Polk Place
