BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:AI in Research: Driving Innovation Forward\n\nDiscover how arti
 ficial intelligence can streamline workflows\, uncover hidden patterns\, an
 d empower breakthroughs in your field. Learn practical applications of AI t
 hrough Odum Institute AIR series that can revolutionize your research proce
 ss.\n\nAI\, for example ChatGPT\, may be used to construct code for softwar
 e packages and programming languages commonly used by social scientists. Ex
 amples include SAS\, Stata and R. The quality of responses has varied to th
 is point and may continue to at the time of the class. Examples will be giv
 en.\n\nYou must have a UNC Chapel Hill Onyen to register and attend this co
 urse. No registration fees required but you must register to secure your sp
 ot and receive the Zoom link.
DTEND:20260924T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260306T215836Z
DTSTART:20260924T170000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
